namespace = POP_Setup
country_event = { 
	id = POP_Setup.001
	title = no_localisation
	desc = no_localisation
	picture = MEIOU_AND_TAXES_eventPicture
	is_triggered_only = yes
	hidden = yes
	immediate = { 
		country_event = { 
			id = POP_StartInit.002
		}
		every_province = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					is_wasteland = no
					NOT = { 
						province_id = 5154
					}
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = aco
				value = 0
			}
		}

					}

			}

				limit = { 
					AND = {

							which = acp

						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = aco
					value = 0.7
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = aco
					value = 0.75
				}

						value = 0.5
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					OR = { 
						region = crimea_region
						region = steppes_region
						region = volga_region
						province_id = 2626
						province_id = 1400

					NOT = { 
						province_id = 283
						province_id = 2535
						province_id = 258
						province_id = 2507
						area = nogai_area
					}
				}
			}

				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						is_variable_equal = { 
							which = acp
							value = 0.5
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = {

			multiply_variable = { 
				which = aco
				which = abr
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = aco
				value = 0.001
			}
			PREV = { 
				change_variable = { 
					which = aco
					which = PREV
				}
			}
		}
		set_variable = { 
			which = acq
			which = aco
		}
		set_variable = { 
			which = aco
			value = 0
		}
		every_province = { 
			limit = { 
				AND = { 
					is_wasteland = no
					NOT = { 
						province_id = 5154
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = acp
						value = 0.5
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					OR = { 
						region = crimea_region
						region = steppes_region
						region = volga_region
						province_id = 2626
						province_id = 1400
						province_id = 160

					NOT = {

						province_id = 2535
						province_id = 258
						province_id = 2507
						area = nogai_area
					}
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = acq
				which = PREV
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = aco
				value = 10
			}
			divide_variable = { 
				which = aco
				which = acq
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = aco
				value = 10000
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = aco
				value = 0.1
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = acq
				value = 0
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						AND = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = aco
								value = 1.1
							}
						}
					}
				}
				change_variable = { 
					which = aco
					value = 1
				}
			}
		}
		set_variable = { 
			which = acq
			value = 0
		}
		every_province = {

					NOT = {

					}
				}
			}

								value = 0.001

				set_variable = { 
					which = aho
					which = aco
				}
			}

				which = aco
				value = 0

		}
